Package org.thymeleaf.templateresolver

Class DefaultTemplateResolver

  • Object
    • org.thymeleaf.templateresolver.AbstractTemplateResolver
      • org.thymeleaf.templateresolver.DefaultTemplateResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITemplateResolver
    public class DefaultTemplateResolver
extends AbstractTemplateResolver

    Implementation of ITemplateResolver that extends AbstractTemplateResolver and acts as a default template resolver, always returning the same specified text in the form of a StringTemplateResource instance.

    This template resolver will consider its resolved templates always cacheable.

    Also, the TemplateMode.HTML template mode will be used by default.

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Daniel Fernández
